{"tid":885672,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"單身耐到覺得自己會孤獨終身....","createTime":"2018-11-01T13:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T08:21:39.000Z","uid":216277,"like":26,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c9cac7560d8bab3fe670a51fd4892f66a03bd835","tid":885672,"uid":216277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T13:26:45.000Z","msg":"拍過第一次拖之後<br />\n斷斷續續都有拖拍<br />\n空窗期未試過半年<br />\n但自從上一個分手之後.......單身左兩年幾<br />\n完全冇遇到心動嘅人<br />\n一來圈子入面冇自己個type<br />\n二來覺得好多人玩玩下<br />\n遇過幾次人地鍾意我 但自己真係零感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時候諗翻都唔記得拍拖係咩感覺<br />\n對戀愛好期待但又死心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前排仲同老豆老母講 我應該都結唔到婚 要成世痴住你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵唔到自己鍾意嘅人真係好慘<br />\n連單戀嘅感覺都體會唔到"},{"pid":"eae672f11fc527f45a1b7e8e82d8e904486f7ee5","tid":885672,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T13:27:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c11ec9e36e621e7e21eca8cc4d0c62b58d758774","tid":885672,"uid":216277,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"eae672f11fc527f45a1b7e8e82d8e904486f7ee5","tid":885672,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T13:27:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T13:30:21.000Z","msg":"系Y 莪吾識中文"},{"pid":"77817d8aa131581d035784134f090f011e093aa4","tid":885672,"uid":30098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T13:31:29.000Z","msg":"有人成世未拍過拖"},{"pid":"a7b3eafc3e66a9f365fb4fb594a3ba7e85ac1653","tid":885672,"uid":2154,"like":6,